{
  "stem": "1042.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He use to bring us even parcels, what was not for Jews because shoes wasn't allowed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Polish people also there in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were working, you know, political.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were against the Germans, so they put them there in the camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this one, he said, you-- because you're working like this, and you fix the machines, you will go to Brnenec.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I make for you that you got the permission to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the owner of Brnenec to go was Schindler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the next two days, he called up Schindler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Schindler was a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No, he was not a soldier, an SS officer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he came, and he told me right away, he told them before what I am doing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, you belong to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Next month or in three, four weeks, goes transportation to Brnenec.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you take all the machines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I make you, right now, responsible for the machines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you can put in whatever you have here, some spares, some [INAUDIBLE] or whatever, because the machines they go straight to Sudetenland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Brnenec.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was already 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he told me this-- and he told me [NON-ENGLISH], not [NON-ENGLISH], like they used to say in German and Polish-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said me, like we say here, you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we say to everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a very, very nice man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he promised me right away that I shall be the one, and there he got also the machines [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the way what I finished in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can't go through all the details because in Plaszow, was killings day by day, thousands of human beings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, it's very hard to talk about it, but I am telling you how I felt.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
